#: ../../../security/auth_providers.rst:30
msgid ""
"`HTTP Basic authentication`_ asks credentials (username and password) "
"using a dialog in the browser. The credentials are sent without any "
"hashing or encryption, so it's recommended to use it with HTTPS."
msgstr ""

