"firewall:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../security/auth_providers.rst:86
msgid ""
"That's it! Symfony will now be listening for any HTTP basic "
"authentication data. To load user information, it will use your "
"configured :doc:`user provider </security/user_provider>`."
msgstr ""

